2.  Enumeration — dig into SMB, LDAP, Kerberos, RPC, shares, users.
3.  Foothold — obtain credentials or remote shell.
4.  Privilege escalation — local or domain escalation.
5.  Post-exploitation — data collection, lateral movement, persistence .
