AD-focused attacks and escalation techniques
Kerberoast: request service tickets for accounts with SPNs and crack them 
offline. Tools: GetUserSPNs.py (Impacket), Rubeus.

AS-REP Roasting: target users without pre-auth.

ACL abuse and delegation: search for accounts/computers with GenericAll,
WriteDACL, or unconstrained delegation. Tools: BloodHound, PowerView.

Credential reuse: check service configs, scripts, scheduled tasks for re-used creds.




